iveData_Search/production.htm\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Utah</a></li><li data-uniq-id=\"yxw54\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-pmZnY\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"http://www.dep.wv.gov/oil-and-gas/Pages/default.aspx\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">West Virginia</a></li><li data-uniq-id=\"lfyy9\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-aXeS9\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"http://wogcc.state.wy.us/\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Wyoming</a></li></ul><p data-uniq-id=\"uzApq\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-bZwIb\"><br></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id=\"\"><div><div data-brz-translate-text=\"1\"><p data-generated-css=\"brz-css-zNlQO\" data-uniq-id=\"u5JeB\"><strong style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color4),1);\">Additional Reading</strong></p><ul><li data-generated-css=\"brz-css-s3eUX\" data-uniq-id=\"zGVci\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"/oil-gas-measurement\" data-brz-link-type=\"page\">Oil &amp; Gas Measurement</a><span style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color4),1);\"> – Explanation of how oil and gas is measured at the lease and how it relates to payment for royalty owners or mineral owners. Defines MMBTU, MCF, BBL and more.</span></li></ul><p data-generated-css=\"brz-css-pP2vX\" data-uniq-id=\"g9Vl_\"></p><ul><li data-generated-css=\"brz-css-nJps7\" data-uniq-id=\"oRb2d\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"/oil-and-gas-investment-basics\" data-brz-link-type=\"page\">Oil and Gas Investment Basics</a><span style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color4),1);\"> – Short article explaining direct oil &amp; gas investment basics for those considering investing in oil/gas wells. Topics include ri